ENCHANTMENT
Type: Sub-sphere of Magic
Commands: spells, cast
See also: <spellhelp>, <help player documents magic>

You can cast a variety of enchantments. Enchantment spells might blind an opponent, increase your strength, or spy on an enemy from afar. They rarely directly damage an opponenent. 

An enchanter is also needed to repair the shield system on a sailing vessel.
